Description: A powerful warrior engulfed in flames, feared by all.
A mystical guardian that freezes enemies in their tracks.
A knight infused with the power of lightning, striking swiftly.
A silent killer who moves unseen in the darkness.
A towering guardian of stone, slow but powerful.
A spellcaster who controls the tides and rain.
A legendary bird that rises from its own ashes.
A towering beast of ice that chills enemies to the bone.
A dragon that commands the storms with devastating power.
A mischievous goblin that attacks in swarms.
A dark sorcerer who raises the dead to fight.
A warrior blessed by the gods, wielding holy power.
A skilled archer with unparalleled precision.
A savage warrior who grows stronger in battle.
A master of black magic, feared for her powerful curses.
